casebody.data:
William S. BARKER et al., Appellants, v. C. A. SHEEDY, as Receiver of The Pickwick Corporation, Appellee. No. 8174. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. April 16, 1936. Gibson, Dunn & Crutcher, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. Chandler, Wright & Ward, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, GARRECPIT, and MATHEWS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed, without costs; mandate forthwith.
